---
By: Louise L.Hay
Locus:
  Page: 299
  Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Light
---
The sun is always shining. Even though clouds may come along and obscure
the sun for a while, the sun is always shining. The sun never stops
shining. And even though the earth turns, and the sun appears to go down,
it really never stops shining.
